data.description: Awesome 3 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath split floor plan located on a quiet street in Burleson ISD. Updated laminate wood floors flow through out the main living areas. Large primary living with wood burning fireplace and tons of natural light. Just off the living is the kitchen.Kitchen features crisp white cabinets, granite counter tops, custom backslash and eat in kitchen area. Large game room at back of the home makes for a great entertaining space! Outback enjoy your very own retreat with in-ground swimming pool. Cabana style covered patio equipped with a mini fridge, multiple ceiling fans, vent hood in place if you want to add a stove, a bar large enough to seat 4, and a half bath! Located right around the corner from the Burleson Recreation Center & walking trails.
